SECTION 80. IC 12-17.2-5-6.3, AS AMENDED BY P.L.74-2022,
SECTION 11, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 6.3. (a) To qualify for a license to operate a class
I child care home under this chapter, a person must do the following:
