circumstances hunter attends the course of instruction in hunter
education offered by the department or the department's agent under
IC 14-22-35.
(g) A special circumstances hunter must:
(1) comply with the requirements under this article, including
obtaining a valid hunting license issued under IC 14-22-11, and
