under subsection (f), the state department shall release a copy of the
paternity affidavit to the requesting attorney or agency.
SECTION 109. IC 16-39-2-6, AS AMENDED BY SEA 222-2026,
SECTION 94, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE
JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 6. (a) Without the consent of the patient, the
patient's mental health record may only be disclosed as follows:
(1) To individuals who meet the following conditions:
(A) Are employed by:
(i) the provider at the same facility or agency;
(ii) a managed care provider (as defined in IC 12-7-2-127);
IC 12-7-2.1-219); or
