SECTION 207. IC 31-34-20-1.5, AS AMENDED BY P.L.186-2025,
SEA 80 — CC 1

288
SECTION 161, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS
[EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 1.5. (a) Except as provided in
subsection (d), the juvenile court may not enter a dispositional decree
