SECTION 306. IC 22-3-2-2.6, AS ADDED BY HEA 1098-2026,
SEA 80 — CC 1

384
SECTION 4, IS AMENDED TO AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE JULY
1, 2026]: Sec. 2.6. (a) As used in this section, "work based learning
program" has the meaning set forth in IC 20-20-38.6-3.
IC 20-20.5-11.5-3.
(b) Except as provided in subsection (c), a student who performs
services for an employer as part of a work based learning program:
(1) is entitled to compensation and benefits under IC 22-3-2
through IC 22-3-6; and
(2) may not recover any additional benefit otherwise payable as
